::Prowl::

Prowl grins at Iron Raptor's suggestion, leaning closer as she tightens her 
hold around him for a second. The idea appealed to him, bringing back 
memories of their time in her quarters in the Ark, when they had been 
distracted by a Predacon attack.

"Let's get you repaired, love," he says softly, leaning in to kiss her, "And 
then I can show you my quarters. We can share them if you want..."

He starts to walk off again, pulling Iron Raptor gently along.
